race.description: Bodalla Pub Country Boosted Showcase Hcp (C1)
race.comment: SHE'S THE KEY (6) was specked from 41.0 to 18.0 first-up and the money was right as she closed well to get up for second over 900m at Queanbeyan. Better suited out to this trip on a track with less quirks. Looks hard to hold out. BOOM IN THE DARK (2) led and gave a kick but found one better over 1100m at Goulburn last time out. On an eight-day back-up and his only win came at this stage of the campaign. Ready to peak today. THREEFOLD (3) returns from a 315-day spell. Filled a placing over this course and distance at the start of last prep, albeit off a shorter lay-off. Lightly raced mare worth monitoring for market support. SMASHING LULU (5) is back from an 18-week break. Flew late to win her maiden over this course and distance at the beginning of last prep. Progressive type who can win without surprising. COMMANDORO (7) will be giving them a start but while fresh could be a surprise packet. CASHBOOK (1) resumes and is another with claims.
